title: Tennessee Senator Bill Hagerty
itunes:title: Tennessee Senator Bill Hagerty
description:
Bloomberg Chief Washington Correspondent Kevin Cirilli spoke with former U.S. Ambassador to Japan and Tennessee Republican Senator Bill Hagerty. They spoke about the stimulus bill, re-opening the country and U.S. reliance on global supply chains.
